gobblin.data.management.retention.version.finder

Class FileLevelTimestampVersionFinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.data.management.retention.version.finder.FileLevelTimestampVersionFinder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VersionFinder<TimestampedDatasetVersion>

    public class FileLevelTimestampVersionFinder
extends Object
implements VersionFinder<TimestampedDatasetVersion>
    VersionFinder that uses the most nested file, or directory if no file exists, level modifiedTimestamp under the datasetRoot path to find DatasetVersions, and represents each version as TimestampedDatasetVersion using the file level path and modifiedTimestamp.
